Arsenal key
A thief nicknamed Baldie managed to steal the key from the Governor's arsenal. It must be returned to the Governor.
#subobj  1
Finding Baldie
A thief nicknamed Baldie lives in the village to the west of the big lake. Any stranger would find himself very unwelcome there!
#subobj  2
Killing Baldie
You must kill Baldie to get the key to the Governor's arsenal.
#subobj  3
Getting the arsenal key
Take the arsenal key from Baldie's corpse.